resources.string: In case of payment by cheque and return unpaid, Rs. 500 towards cheque return and penalty charge will be charged.

We request you to follow our payment guideline. If in case, your payment gets delayed, you are liable for a late fee penalty. Once, you have exceeded the date, for the first seven days you would be charged Rs/-500, from 8th day till 14th day Rs/- 1000, and on the 15th day your services will be suspended.
All the cheques / drafts will be made in favour of "V2IDEAS.COM".
Disputes, if any, are subject to Surat Jurisdiction only
